Package: code-remote
Version: __VERSION__
Architecture: __ARCH__
Maintainer: pigri <david@papp.ai>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: screen
Homepage: https://github.com/pigri/code-remote
Description: Remote control for detached Claude Code sessions
 REST API and the crctl CLI to launch and manage detached Claude Code
 sessions over GNU screen. Ships per-user systemd units for an optional
 remote edge (ngrok) fronted by a Synapse WAF.
 .
 crctl works locally out of the box (no API or token). The API/WAF/ngrok
 path additionally needs the `claude` and `synapse` binaries.
